headline: How Is KLA Corporation’s Stock Performance Compared to Other Semiconductor Stocks?
summary: Despite KLA Corporation’s strong outperformance relative to its industry peers over the past year, analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on the stock’s future prospects.
